---
title: Garlicky Pork Meatballs in Spiced Tomato Sauce with Cheese, Basmati Rice and Peas
description: These Garlicky Pork Meatballs in Spiced Tomato Sauce are a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
